ue bodies, and graphic violence.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aArtists' materialszIndiazMumbai. 0aCinematographyxSpecial effectsy20th century. 0aHorror filmsxProduction and directionzIndiazMumbai. 0aHorror filmszIndiazMumbaiy20th century. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2024z978311079135840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520392298?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520392298423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520392298/original  a978-3-11-079135-8  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2024b2024  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles